  <chapter id='libgwy-one-dimensional-data'>
    <title>One-Dimensional Data</title>
    <para>
      Two basic data objects represent one-dimensional data:
      <link linkend='GwyLine'><type>GwyLine</type></link>
      represents data in a regular one-dimensional grid, while
      <link linkend='GwyCurve'><type>GwyCurve</type></link>
      represents a function of one variable sampled at arbitrary points.
    </para>
